{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"debug":1},true],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"zotero":1,"inscriptions":5},{"title":2,"date":3,"citation":4},"Case e terra a Kamarina e Morgantina nel III–II sec. a.C.","1989","\u003Cspan>Giacomo Manganaro, «Case e terra a Kamarina e Morgantina nel III–II sec. a.C.», \u003Ci>La Parola del Passato\u003C/i> 44 (1989): 189–216\u003C/span>",[6,104,148,180,216,247,277,312,346,376,408,445,476,505],{"file":7,"uri":7,"title":8,"status":9,"editionAuthor":11,"type":12,"objectType":16,"material":20,"condition":24,"layoutDesc":26,"handNote":35,"date":37,"places":42,"geo":51,"country":55,"region":56,"settlement":57,"repository":58,"idno":62,"textLang":64,"facsimile":68,"provenance":44,"letterHeights":75,"publications":76,"zotero":83,"keywords":90,"html":103},"ISic030001","Contract for the sale of a house",{"_":10},"draft",null,{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},"Private contract","#function.legal.private.contract","https://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/375.html",{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},"lamina","#object.lamina","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/145.html",{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},"Lead","#material.metal.lead","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/108.html",{"ana":25},"#condition.damaged condition.fragments.contiguous",{"layout":27},{"p":28,"rs":29,"damage":33},"The lines of text begin at the left edge of the sheet and run across to the right edge without margins. Although the original upper edge of the tablet is lost, the beginning of the text is likely preserved; it is unclear what the top margin was. The bottom margin is approximately as tall as is the text itself, i.e. the text ends around the midpoint of the sheet as currently preserved. The first four lines fill the width of the sheet and when the line ends in the middle of a word either the final letters are squeezed in (L.1) or the word is interrupted (L.3).",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},"engraved","#execution.engraved","https://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/3.html",{"ana":34},"#text_condition.incomplete",{"dimensions":36},[11,11],{"_":38,"notBefore":39,"notAfter":40,"evidence":41},"2nd century BCE",-200,-101,"lettering",[43,47],{"_":44,"type":45,"ref":46},"Morgantina","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462372",{"_":48,"type":49,"ref":50},"Aidone","modern","http://www.geonames.org/6537793/aidone.html",[52],[53,54],37.43067,14.47945,"Italy","Sicily","Ragusa",{"_":59,"role":60,"ref":61},"Museo Archeologico Ibleo","museum","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/091",{"type":63},"inventory",{"_":65,"mainLang":66,"languages":67},"Ancient Greek","grc",[65],{"n":69,"url":70,"height":71,"width":72,"desc":73,"surfaceType":74},"screen","ISic030001_tiled.tif","2195px","3212px","Composite photo of the inscribed surface, R. Souza, courtesy Museo Regionale Interdisciplinare di Ragusa","front",[],[77,77,77,78,79,80,81,82],"Supplementum epigraphicum graecum, 1923-","Bulletin épigraphique, 1888-","Manganaro, 1989, Case e terra a Kamarina e Morgantina nel III–II sec. a.C.","Game, 2009, Actes de vente dans le monde grec. Témoignages épigraphiques des ventes immobilières","Dubois, 2008, IGDS2","Souza, 2016, Hellenistic Sicilian real estate contracts inscribed on lead tablets: new readings and implications for the economic independence of women",[84,84,84,85,86,87,88,89],"F2GG87EQ","77P5MNIR","SIK4QJV4","H87ZNHMA","SM2KDHZC","BKZKNUPN",[91,92,93,94,17,95,96,97,98,99,100,101,102,66],"isic030001","contract for the sale of a house",{"_":10},"private contract","lead","morgantina","aidone","italy","sicily","ragusa","museo archeologico ibleo","ancient greek","Text encoding: Randall Souza, edition source:",{"file":105,"uri":105,"title":106,"status":107,"editionAuthor":11,"type":108,"objectType":109,"material":110,"condition":111,"layoutDesc":113,"handNote":118,"date":120,"places":121,"geo":127,"country":55,"region":56,"settlement":57,"repository":131,"idno":132,"textLang":134,"provenance":123,"letterHeights":136,"publications":137,"zotero":140,"keywords":143,"html":103},"ISic030051","Contract for the sale of land",{"_":10},{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},{"ana":112},"#condition.damaged",{"layout":114},{"p":115,"rs":116,"damage":117},"The lines of text begin at the left edge of the sheet (a margin of ca. 1-2 mm) and run across to the right edge leaving a right margin as narrow as ca. 1-2 mm (L.6) or as wide as ca. 7 mm (LL. 5, 9, 11): an effort was made to avoid ending a line in the middle of a word but this has happened at least between L. 1 and L. 2, and again between L. 8 and L. 9. Top margin ca. 1-2 mm; bottom margin unknown (support is broken along the entire bottom edge).",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},{"ana":34},{"dimensions":119},[11,11],{"_":38,"notBefore":39,"notAfter":40,"evidence":41},[122,125],{"_":123,"type":45,"ref":124},"Kamarina","https://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462126",{"_":123,"type":49,"ref":126},"http://sws.geonames.org/8063309",[128],[129,130],36.8718784874,14.4483234195,{"_":59,"role":60,"ref":61},{"_":133,"type":63},"8013",{"_":65,"mainLang":66,"languages":135},[65],[],[77,78,138,79,139],"Manganaro, 1977, Tavolette di piombo inscritte della Sicilia greca","Dubois, 1989, IGDS1",[84,85,141,86,142],"F5HM44RP","RWXNUFEX",[144,145,146,94,17,95,147,147,98,99,100,101,102,66],"isic030051","contract for the sale of land",{"_":10},"kamarina",{"file":149,"uri":149,"title":150,"status":151,"editionAuthor":11,"type":152,"objectType":153,"material":154,"condition":155,"layoutDesc":156,"handNote":161,"date":163,"places":164,"geo":167,"country":55,"region":56,"settlement":57,"repository":169,"idno":170,"textLang":171,"provenance":123,"letterHeights":173,"publications":174,"zotero":175,"keywords":176,"html":103},"ISic030052","Contract for the sale of property",{"_":10},{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},{"ana":112},{"layout":157},{"p":158,"rs":159,"damage":160},"The text fills all the preserved surface; this appears to be a fragment from the center of the original lead sheet and no information about the margins or original extent of the text is preserved.",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},{"ana":34},{"dimensions":162},[11,11],{"_":38,"notBefore":39,"notAfter":40,"evidence":41},[165,166],{"_":123,"type":45,"ref":124},{"_":123,"type":49,"ref":126},[168],[129,130],{"_":59,"role":60,"ref":61},{"_":133,"type":63},{"_":65,"mainLang":66,"languages":172},[65],[],[77,138,79,139],[84,141,86,142],[177,178,179,94,17,95,147,147,98,99,100,101,102,66],"isic030052","contract for the sale of property",{"_":10},{"file":181,"uri":181,"title":182,"status":183,"editionAuthor":11,"type":184,"objectType":185,"material":186,"condition":187,"layoutDesc":188,"handNote":193,"date":195,"places":199,"geo":202,"country":55,"region":56,"settlement":57,"repository":204,"idno":205,"textLang":207,"provenance":123,"letterHeights":209,"publications":210,"zotero":211,"keywords":212,"html":103},"ISic030053","Contract for the sale of a house and a shop",{"_":10},{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},{"ana":112},{"layout":189},{"p":190,"rs":191,"damage":192},"The left margin is not preserved but the first letters of most lines are preserved; the damage to the top has destroyed some of the text of L.1, and the ancient folds have damaged some of the text body. The right margin is entirely preserved and the bottom margin partially preserved.",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},{"ana":34},{"dimensions":194},[11,11],{"_":196,"notBefore":197,"notAfter":198,"evidence":41},"ca. 300 BCE",-350,-251,[200,201],{"_":123,"type":45,"ref":124},{"_":123,"type":49,"ref":126},[203],[129,130],{"_":59,"role":60,"ref":61},{"_":206,"type":63},"4470",{"_":65,"mainLang":66,"languages":208},[65],[],[79,139],[86,142],[213,214,215,94,17,95,147,147,98,99,100,101,102,66],"isic030053","contract for the sale of a house and a shop",{"_":10},{"file":217,"uri":217,"title":150,"status":218,"editionAuthor":11,"type":219,"objectType":220,"material":221,"condition":222,"layoutDesc":223,"handNote":228,"date":230,"places":231,"geo":234,"country":55,"region":56,"settlement":57,"repository":236,"idno":237,"textLang":239,"provenance":123,"letterHeights":241,"publications":242,"zotero":243,"keywords":244,"html":103},"ISic030054",{"_":10},{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},{"ana":112},{"layout":224},{"p":225,"rs":226,"damage":227},"Only the right margin of the text is preserved; the last preserved line of text may well be the final line of the original due to the lack of visible letters below it and the fact that the line runs closest to the right edge of the lamina (perhaps in an effort to avoid running onto a new line); the full bottom margin is not preserved. Top and left margins are unknown. No word breaks at line ends.",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},{"ana":34},{"dimensions":229},[11,11],{"_":196,"notBefore":197,"notAfter":198,"evidence":41},[232,233],{"_":123,"type":45,"ref":124},{"_":123,"type":49,"ref":126},[235],[129,130],{"_":59,"role":60,"ref":61},{"_":238,"type":63},"8020",{"_":65,"mainLang":66,"languages":240},[65],[],[79,139],[86,142],[245,178,246,94,17,95,147,147,98,99,100,101,102,66],"isic030054",{"_":10},{"file":248,"uri":248,"title":150,"status":249,"editionAuthor":11,"type":250,"objectType":251,"material":252,"condition":253,"layoutDesc":254,"handNote":259,"date":261,"places":262,"geo":265,"country":55,"region":56,"settlement":57,"repository":267,"idno":268,"textLang":269,"provenance":123,"letterHeights":271,"publications":272,"zotero":273,"keywords":274,"html":103},"ISic030055",{"_":10},{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},{"ana":112},{"layout":255},{"p":256,"rs":257,"damage":258},"No margins are preserved.",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},{"ana":34},{"dimensions":260},[11,11],{"_":196,"notBefore":197,"notAfter":198,"evidence":41},[263,264],{"_":123,"type":45,"ref":124},{"_":123,"type":49,"ref":126},[266],[129,130],{"_":59,"role":60,"ref":61},{"_":238,"type":63},{"_":65,"mainLang":66,"languages":270},[65],[],[79,139],[86,142],[275,178,276,94,17,95,147,147,98,99,100,101,102,66],"isic030055",{"_":10},{"file":278,"uri":278,"title":106,"status":279,"editionAuthor":11,"type":280,"objectType":281,"material":282,"condition":283,"layoutDesc":284,"handNote":289,"date":291,"places":295,"geo":298,"country":55,"region":56,"settlement":300,"repository":301,"textLang":304,"provenance":123,"letterHeights":306,"publications":307,"zotero":308,"keywords":309,"html":103},"ISic030056",{"_":10},{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},{"ana":112},{"layout":285},{"p":286,"rs":287,"damage":288},"The top and right margins are entirely preserved; the bottom margin is preserved in one or two places, and the left margin is preserved at the very top of the text. The text wraps and several words are continued fron one line onto the next, breaking roughly between syllables (Lines 3, 4, 6, 9).",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},{"ana":34},{"dimensions":290},[11,11],{"_":292,"notBefore":293,"notAfter":294,"evidence":41},"ca. 250-200 BCE",-250,-201,[296,297],{"_":123,"type":45,"ref":124},{"_":123,"type":49,"ref":126},[299],[129,130],"unknown",{"_":302,"role":303},"private collection","private",{"_":65,"mainLang":66,"languages":305},[65],[],[77,79,81],[84,86,88],[310,145,311,94,17,95,147,147,98,99,300,302,102,66],"isic030056",{"_":10},{"file":313,"uri":313,"title":314,"status":315,"editionAuthor":11,"type":316,"objectType":317,"material":318,"condition":319,"layoutDesc":320,"handNote":325,"date":327,"places":328,"geo":331,"country":55,"region":56,"settlement":57,"repository":333,"idno":334,"textLang":335,"provenance":123,"letterHeights":337,"publications":338,"zotero":340,"keywords":342,"html":103},"ISic030057","Contract for the sale of a house and related structures",{"_":10},{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},{"ana":112},{"layout":321},{"p":322,"rs":323,"damage":324},"The top of the sheet is damaged and the first line of text is not well preserved, but does appear to be the first line of the document. The right margin is entirely preserved. The bottom of the sheet is damaged but the final preserved line of text does appear to be the last line of the document. The left margin is unknown, and it is an open question how much text is lost on the left side (see below in commentary). The text wraps and several words are continued fron one line onto the next, breaking roughly between syllables (Lines 4, 5).",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},{"ana":34},{"dimensions":326},[11,11],{"_":292,"notBefore":293,"notAfter":294,"evidence":41},[329,330],{"_":123,"type":45,"ref":124},{"_":123,"type":49,"ref":126},[332],[129,130],{"_":59,"role":60,"ref":61},{"type":63},{"_":65,"mainLang":66,"languages":336},[65],[],[77,78,79,81,339],"Souza, 2022, More new readings of Hellenistic Sicilian real estate contracts involving women",[84,85,86,88,341],"2RKAGTPR",[343,344,345,94,17,95,147,147,98,99,100,101,102,66],"isic030057","contract for the sale of a house and related structures",{"_":10},{"file":347,"uri":347,"title":150,"status":348,"editionAuthor":11,"type":349,"objectType":350,"material":351,"condition":352,"layoutDesc":353,"handNote":358,"date":360,"places":361,"geo":364,"country":55,"region":56,"settlement":57,"repository":366,"idno":367,"textLang":368,"provenance":123,"letterHeights":370,"publications":371,"zotero":372,"keywords":373,"html":103},"ISic030058",{"_":10},{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},{"ana":112},{"layout":354},{"p":355,"rs":356,"damage":357},"Only the bottom margin is preserved",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},{"ana":34},{"dimensions":359},[11,11],{"_":292,"notBefore":293,"notAfter":294,"evidence":41},[362,363],{"_":123,"type":45,"ref":124},{"_":123,"type":49,"ref":126},[365],[129,130],{"_":59,"role":60,"ref":61},{"type":63},{"_":65,"mainLang":66,"languages":369},[65],[],[77,79,81,339],[84,86,88,341],[374,178,375,94,17,95,147,147,98,99,100,101,102,66],"isic030058",{"_":10},{"file":377,"uri":377,"title":378,"status":379,"editionAuthor":11,"type":380,"objectType":381,"material":382,"condition":383,"layoutDesc":384,"handNote":389,"date":391,"places":392,"geo":395,"country":55,"region":56,"settlement":57,"repository":397,"idno":398,"textLang":399,"provenance":123,"letterHeights":401,"publications":402,"zotero":403,"keywords":404,"html":103},"ISic030059","Contract label?",{"_":10},{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},{"ana":112},{"layout":385},{"p":386,"rs":387,"damage":388},"The short two-word text sits in the middle of the sheet and was apparently the only writing on it.",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},{"ana":34},{"dimensions":390},[11,11],{"_":292,"notBefore":293,"notAfter":294,"evidence":41},[393,394],{"_":123,"type":45,"ref":124},{"_":123,"type":49,"ref":126},[396],[129,130],{"_":59,"role":60,"ref":61},{"type":63},{"_":65,"mainLang":66,"languages":400},[65],[],[79,81],[86,88],[405,406,407,94,17,95,147,147,98,99,100,101,102,66],"isic030059","contract label?",{"_":10},{"file":409,"uri":409,"title":410,"status":411,"editionAuthor":11,"type":412,"objectType":413,"material":414,"condition":415,"layoutDesc":416,"handNote":421,"date":423,"places":424,"geo":429,"country":55,"region":56,"settlement":300,"repository":433,"textLang":435,"provenance":44,"letterHeights":437,"publications":438,"zotero":439,"keywords":440,"html":103},"ISic030060","Contract for the sale of a vinyard and equipment",{"_":10},{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},{"ana":112},{"layout":417},{"p":418,"rs":419,"damage":420},"The left side of the text appears to be completely preserved even though the left edge of the sheet moves diagonally (relative to the lines of the text) to the right going from top to bottom; the left margin of the text thus seems to be following this irregular edge, which suggests that the text was engraved on the sheet after it took this irregular form. The text appears to wrap but only at the ends of the first two lines which are restored and from Line 6 to Line 7 which is completely preserved; the line breaks are between syllables.",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},{"ana":34},{"dimensions":422},[11,11],{"_":292,"notBefore":293,"notAfter":294,"evidence":41},[425,427],{"_":44,"type":45,"ref":426},"https://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462372",{"_":44,"type":49,"ref":428},"http://sws.geonames.org/2524052",[430],[431,432],37.430596,14.479485,{"_":434,"role":303},"In a private collection",{"_":65,"mainLang":66,"languages":436},[65],[],[77,78,79,81],[84,85,86,88],[441,442,443,94,17,95,96,96,98,99,300,444,102,66],"isic030060","contract for the sale of a vinyard and equipment",{"_":10},"in a private collection",{"file":446,"uri":446,"title":447,"status":448,"editionAuthor":11,"type":449,"objectType":450,"material":451,"condition":452,"layoutDesc":453,"handNote":458,"date":460,"places":461,"geo":464,"country":55,"region":56,"settlement":57,"repository":466,"textLang":467,"provenance":44,"letterHeights":469,"publications":470,"zotero":471,"keywords":472,"html":103},"ISic030062","Contract for the sale of houses",{"_":10},{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},{"ana":112},{"layout":454},{"p":455,"rs":456,"damage":457},"The left side of the text appears to be completely preserved, as does the top of the text (even though the support is partially damaged at the top). Right margin of text not preserved, nor is the bottom of the text preserved.",{"_":30,"ana":31,"ref":32},{"ana":34},{"dimensions":459},[11,11],{"_":292,"notBefore":293,"notAfter":294,"evidence":41},[462,463],{"_":44,"type":45,"ref":426},{"_":44,"type":49,"ref":428},[465],[431,432],{"_":59,"role":60,"ref":61},{"_":65,"mainLang":66,"languages":468},[65],[],[77,79,81,339],[84,86,88,34